Release Info:

This unlocks pre-order downloadable content:
   
-> Call of Duty: Advanced Warfare - SP Exo Upgrade
   
READNFO:
   
We apologize for the bad crack we packed into our initial release, after our testers greenlighted the game for pre.
     
Since our crack only suffered from a wrong .ini file, this DLC Unlocker can also fix the "you need 5mb free space..." error message you may have seen after starting a new game.
   
Meanwhile RELOADED released a proper crack, which should work fine too.
Kudos for being faster on the fix :)

Install Notes:

- Extract
- Copy unlocker to your installdir
- Play 
   
Notes: This unlocker requires: CODEX release of Call of Duty: AW  
   
      
Block game exe in your firewall to prevent the game from trying to go online
